			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b><a href="http://www.michaelcanfield.net/">By Michael Canfield</a>.</b><br />
Read by <a href="http://www.dragonpage.com/">Evo Terra</a>.<br /></p>

<p><i>        I won&#8217;t kid you, the main reason I contracted to upload this biography is the money. I want a way out of my baby body&#8211;expensive surgery. Thank you for buying this link: even if you don&#8217;t like what I have to say, you&#8217;ve helped an old actor out.</i></p>

